recommendations.proposed_change:
Declare `concurrency:
  group: ${{ github.workflow }}-${{ inputs.version }}
  cancel-in-progress: false` near the top of each snapshot workflow so only one run per version executes at a time; optionally add a broader `${{ github.workflow }}-latest` group to drop superseded manual dispatches.

